{"word":"ἐπαείδω","slug":"ἐπαείδω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπαείδω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:contracted, contraction'>contr.</a> attic <el>-ᾴδω</el>) (<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-άσομαι</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to sing to</i> or <i>in accompaniment</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to sing as an incantation</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>;—<a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a>, <el>ἐπαείδων</el> <i>by means of charms</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}